Metadata-Version: 2.4
Name: g1-controller
Version: 0.1.0
Summary: Unitree G1 arm controller wrapper (LowCmd/LowState) with interpolation and safety limits
Requires-Python: >=3.9
Description-Content-Type: text/markdown
Requires-Dist: numpy
Requires-Dist: unitree-sdk2py

# g1-controller

## Install (editable)
```bash
pip install -e .
```

## AXES INFO
```
# ==== WAIST ====
# WAIST_YAW   : +左回り / -右回り                range[-90, +90]    normal=0
# WAIST_ROLL  : +左曲げ / -右曲げ(ロボット視点)    range[-20, +20]    normal=0
# WAIST_PITCH : +お辞儀 / -反り返り(危ない)        range[0, +30]      normal=0

# ==== LEFT ARM ====
# L_SHOULDER_PITCH : +前 / -後ろ                  range[-120, +120]  normal=0
# L_SHOULDER_ROLL  : +脇上げ / -脇閉め            range[-30, +110]   normal=0
# L_SHOULDER_YAW   : +外回り / -内回り            range[-90, +90]    normal=0
# L_ELBOW          : +前方曲げ / -背面曲げ        range[-10, +120]   normal=0
# L_WRIST_ROLL     : +外側 / -内側                range[-90, +90]    normal=0
# L_WRIST_SIDE(BEND): +前方曲げ / -背面曲げ       range[-90, +90]    normal=0
# L_WRIST_YAW      : +外側曲げ / -内側曲げ        range[-90, +90]    normal=0

# ==== RIGHT ARM ====
# R_SHOULDER_PITCH : +前 / -後ろ                  range[-120, +120]  normal=0
# R_SHOULDER_ROLL  : +脇上げ / -脇閉め            range[-30, +110]   normal=0
# R_SHOULDER_YAW   : +外回り / -内回り            range[-90, +90]    normal=0
# R_ELBOW          : +前方曲げ / -背面曲げ        range[-10, +120]   normal=0
# R_WRIST_ROLL     : +外側 / -内側                range[-90, +90]    normal=0
# R_WRIST_SIDE(BEND): +前方曲げ / -背面曲げ       range[-90, +90]    normal=0
# R_WRIST_YAW      : +外側曲げ / -内側曲げ        range[-90, +90]    normal=0
```

## how to use
```python
from g1_controller import G1ArmController

arm.start()
arm = G1ArmController()
arm.set_axes({22:90, 15:90, 25:60, 18:60, 28:-30}, 3.0)
arm.set_all_axes_to_zero(2.0)
arm.stop()
